class Me:
  def __init__(self, name, pronouns, codes, tools):
    self.name = name
    self.pronouns = pronouns
    self.codes = codes
    self.tools = tools
        
this_is_my = Me("Júlio Billet", "pronouns = they/them", "codes = Python", "tools = Replit.com, Visual Studio Code, Sublime Text, PyCharm")
